name: The story is as old as the world: a little man with big ambitions overcomes difficulties, gets into conflicts and experiences disasters. Despite everything, a man learns, grows up and challenges the whole world. Rodinka will have to go to great lengths to achieve her dreams.
Become the greatest actress of all time

When she visits the tailor in Algrad, Rodinka sees again the beautiful plaid dress she liked in Brungen. It costs even more here, but Rodinka can't wait any longer. She decides to save up and buy the dress, no matter what it costs.
Sometimes small things become the cause and catalyst for massive change... but Rodinka just had to pee.
I peed under the bush. It wasn't great, but at least I didnt pee myself in front of everyone.
Run to the forest and pee
Rodinka falls off a cliff, loses consciousness and wakes up in the middle of a dense forest. No one responds to her cries for help, which means she has to find a way out of this situation on her own.
I got out of the forest but the caravan has already gone. Didnt they notice my absence?! At least I can still sneak back.
I got to Zalesje. Now I need to find the caravan and sneak back like nothing happened.
I found the caravan. But I failed to sneak into my tent undetected.
Get to the road through the woods

Stories about witches have always inspired girls all over the kingdom, only no miracles have ever happened in their lives. One day Rodinka finds a spell book that can make a fairy tale come true. But will Squirrel learn to cast spells and become a real witch?
I have found the spellbook, but the spell didn't work. I must be doing something wrong. I need to find someone who knows magic and can help me.

What do you do when you realize you don't remember anything from your past? Will you try to remember? Will you look to others for answers? Will you just go on with your life, ignoring it? These are the kinds of questions Rodinka will have to answer.

Important people do important things, and unimportant things fall on the shoulders of their subordinates. Rodinka is not a subordinate of the chief of Zalesje, but she really needs to get to one house, which means she has to work as a delivery girl.
Sveta didn't have the right flowers with her, so I would have to dig them up myself at her house.
Difret isn't ready to trust me with a bottle of his best wine. First I would have to go to the church and get all the empty bottles I could find.
The chief of Zalesje asked me for help. He needed the wine, the flowers, and the key. I've handled everything.
It's just that I didn't get the wine too fair and square.

A creepy house, a mad scientist, bone-chilling experiments - what more do you need for a great story? A girl, of course! A naive young babe who will be sacrificed for the sake of scientific progress... or not?

The troupe has an important performance today, but Moriarty is drunk again, so much so that he is not able to get out of bed. Will the drink according to the Lathim's recipe be able to sober up this fool?

Rarely in life does one get the chance to receive a benefit once and for all. Rodinka has a chance to keep her gift, but is it a boon or a dummy?
Sometimes people do terrible things to achieve their goals. Destroying Lordy's gift is one of them. Will Rodinka do it? Will she regret it?
In any crime, there is a victim and a perpetrator. But who's the perpetrator here? Who is the victim? And was there a crime? That's what Rodinka has to figure out.
Speak your mind to the sheriff
